  <title>CITYGCS.CENTRELINE_BIKEWAY_OD</title>
  <abstract>The Toronto Cycling Map shows marked bicycle lanes, sharrows, signed bicycle routes and off-road paths. It also shows suggested routes and connections in areas where routes have not yet been designated as part of the Bikeway Network. The suggested routes and connections have been identified in consultation with experienced Toronto cyclists and the Toronto Cycling Advisory Committee.

On and off-street bikeways, suggested routes and other connections found on the Toronto Cycling Map.</abstract>
